Specs for the globe being turned into a speaker

Metal - possibly aluminium (currently unable to drill)

Copper coil: flat adhesive copper + copper wire
Amplifier: Kemo #M034N 6-16V, 40W - http://www.parts-express.com/kemo-m034n-40-watt-universal-mono-amplifier-module--320-554 
Battery: 9V battery, rechargable NiCd
Circuit has a switch and mono input from an aigo mp3 player
Magnets: 10 x Neobdymium ring magnets


